"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-culture-culture-features-australian-olympic-breaker-raygun-1235077337\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByMiles Klee  The moves were downright dizzying at theOlympicsdebut of a new event in Paris on Friday: breaking, more commonly referred to as \\\"breakdancing.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 91, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999994981863, \"rank\": 5.018057656439624e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As with other athletic competitions introduced to the games in recent years, there was plenty of debate as to whether breaking - here organized into a tournament of head-to-head dance battles observed by a panel of judges - can even be called a sport.\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But viewers certainly vibed with the personalities who showed up, even if the formal setting robbed the art form of itsstreet-cool factor.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mixed feelings about Olympic breaking thus far but I am fascinated by Raygun, the 36-year-old  Australian college professor who does research on \\\"dance, gender politics, and the dynamics between theoretical and practical methodologies.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.44950273483625e-33, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9998285978958362, \"rank\": 0.00017139290288207076, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"pic.twitter.com/0wgHLxfcc9  One B-girl on the scene for the women's event (the men will do their spinning on Saturday) particularly fascinated those watching at home.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rachael Gunn, stage name \\\"Raygun,\\\" is a 36-year-old college professor from Australia.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999997040441013, \"rank\": 2.959560906468661e-07, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9900579618046921, \"rank\": 0.010024582602669006, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999983848046524, \"rank\": 1.0706414219638225e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With both a music degree and a PhD in cultural studies, she pursues interdisciplinary research on breaking, street dance, hip-hop, and gender at Macquarie University in Sydney.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7310088209117595e-28, \"text\": \"Macquarie University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999990095603, \"rank\": 9.773524393201283e-10, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with her unusual academic credits, Gunn stands out as 20 years the senior of Australia's competitor in the men's tournament - she and 16-year-oldJeff \\\"J-Attack\\\" Dunneboth won the Oceania breaking championships to qualify for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9900579618046921, \"rank\": 0.010024582602669006, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999983848046524, \"rank\": 1.0706414219638225e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also got into breaking later in life than most who pursue it seriously, entering her first ever battle in 2012.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But perhaps most of all, Gunn, uh,breaksthe mold of this dance genre with creative choices that left spectators stunned.\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9900579618046921, \"rank\": 0.010024582602669006, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could live all my life and never come up with anything as funny as Raygun, the 36-year-old Australian Olympic breakdancerpic.twitter.com/1uPYBxIlh8  As she went up against rivals representing Lithuania, France, and the U.S., social media was abuzz about Raygun's signature kangaroo hops, flabbergasting floor work, and charmingly corny poses.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.44950273483625e-33, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9998285978958362, \"rank\": 0.00017139290288207076, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999481456741466, \"rank\": 5.1846075252472315e-05, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6880246766125874, \"rank\": 0.33650060667785453, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through the entire set, and despite losing each round, her swagger held firm.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That confidence, she explained to CNBC in aninterviewearlier this month, was always going to be key: \\\"The younger competitors are great in their strength, fitness, and explosiveness,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.2566219174573828e-11, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the older ones bring a different level of maturity to the dance.\\\"\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Japan's Ami Yuasa, 25, ended up taking the gold.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9997623982195954, \"rank\": 0.00013518518266863392, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \")Editor's picksThe 250 Greatest Albums of the 21st Century So FarThe 100 Best TV Episodes of All TimeThe 500 Greatest Albums of All Time100 Best Movies of the 21st Century  Give Raygun the gold right now#breakdancingpic.twitter.com/bMtAWEh3xo  This would be me trying to breakdance at the Olympicspic.twitter.com/vgO3K7YeJN  my five year old niece after she says \\\"watch this!\\\"\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \":pic.twitter.com/KBAMSkgltj  One of Gunn's battles was against Dominika \\\"Nicka\\\" Banevi\\u010d, a durag-wearing 17-year-old from Lithuania who went on to claim the silver medal, so she can credibly say she was beaten by one of the best women breakers in the world.\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 3071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2850, \"end\": 2854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9900579618046921, \"rank\": 0.010024582602669006, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2936, \"end\": 2945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999481456741466, \"rank\": 5.1846075252472315e-05, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And her resume is still impressive in its own right: the top-ranked Australian Breaking Association B-girl in 2020 and 2021, she has represented Australia in annual World Breaking Championships around the globe.Trending StoriesJohn Lithgow Knows J.K. Rowling's Anti-Trans Views Will Now Forever Come Up in 'Every Interview'Kevin Spacey's 'Mental Illness' Should Trigger $29.5 Million Payout, 'House of Cards' Trial Jurors HearBTS Nails Its Comeback With 'Arirang'Top Disaster Response Official Claims He Teleported to a Waffle House  But maybe taking home the gold is not the only way to inspire people.\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3140, \"end\": 3150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9998285978958362, \"rank\": 0.00017139290288207076, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 3217, \"end\": 3226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999983848046524, \"rank\": 1.0706414219638225e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 3592, \"end\": 3604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waffle_House\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Waffle House\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waffle_House\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waffle_House\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At its best, the Olympics is supposed to celebrate the sheer variety of human ability and experience.\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun's routines had average people wondering if they, too, could tap into a hidden potential and rise to the top levels of an international sport.\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3778, \"end\": 3784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.44950273483625e-33, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took guts, determination - and, yes, talent - for Gunn to get where she was on Friday.\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 4016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3980, \"end\": 3984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9900579618046921, \"rank\": 0.010024582602669006, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not we want to reach for the stars ourselves?\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd like to personally thank Raygun for making millions of people worldwide think \\\"huh, maybe I can make the Olympics too\\\"pic.twitter.com/p5QlUbkL2w  Yeah, you can keep your sweaty wrestling and snooty equestrian stuff.\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4096, \"end\": 4102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.44950273483625e-33, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 4269, \"end\": 4279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9997470123910794, \"rank\": 0.0002500499702468165, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just can not relate.\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the 2024 Olympics comes to a close, we are riding with Raygun.\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4366, \"end\": 4372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.44950273483625e-33, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to hear it.\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us a tip using our anonymous form.\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rolling Stone is a part of Penske Media Corporation.\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4436, \"end\": 4449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.109019567844746e-20, \"text\": \"Rolling Stone\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\"}, {\"begin\": 4463, \"end\": 4475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penske_Media_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Penske Media\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penske_Media_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penske_Media_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Rolling Stone, LLC.\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4511, \"end\": 4514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999999436872729, \"rank\": 5.631288696562035e-08, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", 